frameDefinitions: A Device or machine is put in (or out of) service either by a volitional Agent or by a Cause event or force acting on the Device.
An Agent pauses in the course of an Activity. ''

An Agent has access to a finite amount of some Resource and uses it in some way to complete a Purpose.
An Employee has a Position doing work in a particular Field, or doing work on a particular Task, for which an Employer gives Compensation to the Employee.
A Person takes leave from his or her routine Activity (such as work or school) for a Duration of time.
